divs: Sighting DetailsWe were snapping off photos of the falls just before lunch and did not see the ufo until we downloaded the photos on the computer. I noticed that there was this dark missle looking thing in the distance and when I zoomed in on it, it did not look like any plane. Thanks, JM
Summary: dark, missle shaped with pointed ends
